                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">Two hundred eighty-eight delicious recipes carefully worked out so that you can reproduce, in your own kitchen, the true flavors of Cajun and Creole dishes. The New Orleans cookbook whose authenticity dependability, and wealth of information have made it a classic.</span>
              
</td></tr></table>
              <table id="CustomerReviewsPanel" class="ReviewSection" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%"><tr><td>
	
                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Customer reviews:</DIV>
                
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Best of the Best</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>7</span>
